Subject: [PATCH v4 09/17] dt-bindings: PCI: dwc: Add clocks/resets common properties
Date:   Thu, 28 Jul 2022 17:34:19 +0300
Message-ID: <20220728143427.13617-10-Sergey.Semin@baikalelectronics.ru>
